column17:
The following post uses the Distract tactic by bringing up an unrelated topic and shifting the focus away from the main issue of defense and military:

@AzerbaijaniCA Dictators who are pure evil #putin #erdogan and Aliyev https://t.co/Gsqw0vSk3r

This post is discussing dictators such as Putin and Erdogan, which are unrelated to the main topic of defense and military actions. By introducing a completely different topic, the post aims to divert attention from the original discussion about the actions of the Aliyev regime in Azerbaijan.
